data.description: Looking for a single-family brick home with 4 bedrooms 2 baths & 3 car garage? Look no further this is it! Spacious Single Story. Kitchen has granite counters, subway tile backsplash. The Primary boasts soaring ceilings, and a spacious en-suite with a separate tub and shower with tile surround, large walk-in closet and double vanities. FULLY SODDED yard, brick on ALL FOUR sides of the home and so much more. Short commute to the Medical Center and Downtown. Stop by the model home to take a tour. CARPET ONLY IN BEDROOMS!!!!!!! LVP VINYL FLOORING THROUGHOUT THE HOME.
